        <p class="mb-4">The primary advantage of dye sublimation for mouse pad printing is unlimited design freedom. Unlike older imprinting methods that are limited to a small print zone in the corner of the pad, dye sublimation covers the entire pad surface with your full-color design, using the same ink process we apply to our <a href="/promotional-items/towels" class="link-notification">custom towels</a> for edge-to-edge coverage on any promotional textile. This means you can use a large, detailed logo, a photographic background, an intricate pattern, or a combination of images and text across the complete pad area, and for clients who want a complete branded desk setup our <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">branded mugs</a> pair naturally with mouse pads in a corporate gift set. The result is a mouse pad that looks like a premium designed product rather than a generic pad with a small logo applied to it.</p>
