        <p>We have no minimum order quantities and can produce mouse pads in standard and extended sizes. Extended size mouse pads that cover a large desk area are popular with gaming and tech-oriented businesses and individuals. Contact us to discuss sizing options and what format makes the most sense for your target audience. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to get started on your custom mouse pad order.</p>
